verbose_text: We quantified mRNA levels of Glut8, Abcd3, Slc39a3, and Slc31a1 (mouse orthologs of CG1208, pmp70, zip1, and ctr1B, respectively), and we found a significant increase in Abcd3, Glut8, and Slc39a3 expression (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY G; t test, p = 0.006562, p = 0.029, and p = 0.019, respectively) upon intestinal Irs1 knockout.
